    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK79">
<l>puṟattuṟup pellā mevaṉceyyum yākkai</l>
<l>yakattuṟup paṉpi lavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will all external limbs do, for those without</l>
<l>love, the limb within the body?</l>
<l>(Alternative interpretation not mentioned by commentators:)</l>
<l>What's the use of all external faculties, for those who lack</l>
<l>love in the inner faculty?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
